articles.author: Devendra Pandey
articles.title: KL Rahul unlikely for Asia Cup, Shreyas Iyer uncertain as selectors unsure about their match fitness - The Indian Express
articles.description: Team for continental event to be picked on Monday, and providing more spin options also on the agenda.
articles.content: KL Rahuls return to the national squad might take some more time as the senior selection committee is likely to leave him out for the Asia Cup, while Shreyas Iyer’s return also hangs in the balance. … [+2534 chars]
